ss='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/cong-nghe-chuyen-dong-memc-xu-huong-va-nhung-bat-loi\/#memc_la_gi\" >MEMC l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-2' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/cong-nghe-chuyen-dong-memc-xu-huong-va-nhung-bat-loi\/#cach_memc_hoat_dong\" >C\u00e1ch MEMC ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/cong-nghe-chuyen-dong-memc-xu-huong-va-nhung-bat-loi\/#uu_diem_nhuoc_diem_cua_memc\" >\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m &amp; Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a MEMC<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/cong-nghe-chuyen-dong-memc-xu-huong-va-nhung-bat-loi\/#cong_nghe_memc_co_can_thiet\" >C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 MEMC c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<blockquote><p>N\u0103m 2022 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh n\u0103ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea5y ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb l\u00e0 MEMC. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ec3n h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb TV v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i Smartphone.\u00a0D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec v\u1ec1 MEMC, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1ecbn chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng, bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c MEMC ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"memc_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>MEMC l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p>MEMC l\u00e0 vi\u1ebft t\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Motion Estimation, Motion Compensation. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u00e8n c\u00e1c khung h\u00ecnh v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa hai khung h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3nh quay \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 khung h\u00ecnh trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3nh. N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m cho c\u1ea3nh quay m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1ea3nh quay m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 h\u01a1n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean h\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u s\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 khung h\u00ecnh trong video, gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed b\u1ea1n \u0111ang xem video <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=B_dE6HPIAJM&amp;t=1s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">YouTube<\/a> \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 30 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y ho\u1eb7c khung h\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i gi\u00e2y. B\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng video b\u1ea1n \u0111ang xem \u1edf 1080p 30 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t 1080p 60 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y. Chuy\u1ec3n sang 60 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y gi\u00fap video xem m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 h\u01a1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ec video c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng.<\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3nh quay 60 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y s\u1ebd tr\u00f4ng tr\u00f4i ch\u1ea3y h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 do b\u1ea1n \u0111ang th\u1ea5y 60 khung h\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i gi\u00e2y, g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i s\u1ed1 khung h\u00ecnh so v\u1edbi 30 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 60 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y, 90 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y ho\u1eb7c 120 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y, c\u1ea3nh quay c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quay \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khung h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu video ho\u1eb7c b\u1ed9 phim ho\u1eb7c t\u1eadp ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang xem kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t 60 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y? \u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu video ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 30 khung h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb m\u1ed7i gi\u00e2y? \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fac c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 MEMC b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-11390 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/memc-copy-755x400.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00d4NG NGH\u1ec6 CHUY\u1ec2N \u0110\u1ed8NG MEMC? XU H\u01af\u1edaNG V\u00c0 NH\u1eeeNG B\u1ea4T L\u1ee2I | INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" width=\"755\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/memc-copy-755x400.jpg 755w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/memc-copy-768x407.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/memc-copy-600x318.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/memc-copy.jpg 980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 755px) 100vw, 755px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach_memc_hoat_dong\"><\/span><strong>C\u00e1ch MEMC ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ebfu thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 MEMC, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee9ng chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ec3 &#8216;m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng&#8217; m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 khung. C\u00e1c khung h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3 n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c khung h\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3nh quay, t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 h\u01a1n, ngay c\u1ea3 khi video g\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quay \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 30 khung h\u00ecnh \/ gi\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 video t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n th\u00e0nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i cao h\u01a1n. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb, thay v\u00ec t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i, MEMC t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khung h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uu_diem_nhuoc_diem_cua_memc\"><\/span><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m &amp; Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a MEMC<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a MEMC l\u00e0 t\u00ednh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>N\u1ed9i dung b\u1ea1n \u0111ang xem hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 50% ho\u1eb7c 100% khung h\u00ecnh, l\u00e0m cho n\u1ed9i dung b\u1ea1n \u0111ang xem tr\u1edf n\u00ean tr\u00f4i ch\u1ea3y v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi MEMC ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m m\u1ecbn chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nhanh th\u01b0\u1eddng li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao nh\u01b0 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, n\u1ed9i suy khung h\u00ecnh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea7u ra cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n<p>Trong <a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/thiet-bi-hien-thi-tuong-tac-lop-hoc\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">INNO Smart TV<\/a>, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 MEMC, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khung h\u00ecnh cao h\u01a1n trong tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ecdn, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m xem trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-11389 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-15-at-11.30.20-582x400.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"371\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-15-at-11.30.20-582x400.png 582w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-15-at-11.30.20-768x527.png 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-15-at-11.30.20-320x220.png 320w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-15-at-11.30.20-600x412.png 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-15-at-11.30.20.png 980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c khung h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean (trong th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c) c\u1ea7n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean TV nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd pin nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>MEMC t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c video \u0111\u00f4i khi tr\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean do c\u00f3 c\u00e1c khung h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u1edf gi\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn n\u1ed9i dung phim gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quay tr\u00ean video k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1, thay v\u00ec phim, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m phi\u1ec1n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch xem n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd theo c\u00e1ch g\u1ed1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quay, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c khung h\u00ecnh m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao TV MEMC th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eaft MEMC n\u1ebfu v\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong_nghe_memc_co_can_thiet\"><\/span><strong>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 MEMC c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh n\u0103ng cao c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i v\u00e0 TV cao c\u1ea5p, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00a0m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng khi b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n ra cho MEMC. Nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng xem m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 th\u00eam v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00fd ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bhay, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n mua 1 chi\u1ebfc TV v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n v\u1ec1 MEMC th\u00ec li\u00ean h\u1ec7 cho INNO \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u0103m 2022 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh n\u0103ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea5y ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb l\u00e0 MEMC. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ec3n h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb TV v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i Smartphone.\u00a0D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec v\u1ec1 MEMC, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":11390,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-11387","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11387","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11387"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11387\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":11406,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11387\/revisions\/11406"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/11390"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11387"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=11387"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=11387"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}